&lt;p&gt;Contracting authority: COOPI &amp;ndash; Cooperazione Internazionale &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description of the contract: &amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

