                                   COOPI Cooperazione Internazionale is an humanitarian, non confessional and independent organization that fights against all kinds of poverty to make the world a better place. Founded in 1965 by Vincenzo Barbieri (Italian &quot;father&quot; of international volunteering), COOPI is based in Milan and it has 20 local offices in the South of the World.
 
It wo...  

